  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Click on <em>Button </em>and you will see opened <em>ColorDialog </em>with <em>CustomColors</em>.&nbsp;Select color and click on Ok button and the dialog will closed and <em>Label BackColor</em> will be changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>ColorDialog </em>dialog box contains <em>CustomColors </em>property that defines the set of custom colors shown in the dialog box.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
